reviews: I have a similar pair of Adidas superstar pants and I much prefer the Starter pants. They are so much lighter than my Adidas pants and I think the material is softer. These are still a little hot if you're wearing them at the height of summer but I can roll up the pant legs and wear them capri-style and they'll stay in place.
